Two elimination phases occur as a result of ramiprilat's potent binding to ACE and slow dissociation from the enzyme. The half life of ramiprilat after multiple daily doses (MDDs) is dose-dependent, ranging from 13-17 hours with 5-10 mg MDDs to 27-36 hours for 2.5 mg MDDs.
